cocaine-native-proxy (0.11.0.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Support of timeouts.
  * Support of multiple locators.
  * Support of multiple cocaine threads. You don't need several native proxies behind one nginx anymore.
  * Helpful monitorings are added.
  * The proxy now can determine application and event via headers.
  * Minor bugfixes.

